topic.title: Someone please help me with using hashcat to crack MD5 hashes
topic.body:
I need help using hashcat to crack a MD5 hash. So I downloaded the big CrackStation cracking list from <https://crackstation.net/crackstation-wordlist-password-cracking-dictionary.htm>

I also got a hashcat rule from <https://github.com/NotSoSecure/password_cracking_rules>
If anyone is good at hashcat and can post me some help, I would appreciate it greatly!
This is the MD5 hash if for some reason u want to look at it: e94ae0a4d879bc1e1570b14af5d5273e
I researched this subject on the web for a while, finding nothing that would work for me, so im coming to you guys for help.
